<h1>Developer Comment</h1> This 'marketing opt in' screen allows users to opt into marketing emails and push notifications once they have logged in. The heading describes the type of messages we will send. They are marketing messages, but we don’t want to use the word ‘marketing’. Another word for 'deals' is 'offers' and with ‘stay one step ahead’ we mean the user will be in a better position as they will get useful updates to help with their travel planning. This is the copy for the primary CTA green button.
